<p>To help families enjoy more positive emotions each day and ensure they feel good in their surroundings, Dr Sharp is challenging families to make a few simple, and affordable, changes that will leave them feeling revitalised.</p>

<p>'From the lighting of a room to ornaments and furniture, there are numerous ways the space we live in affects our happiness, which in turn leads toward better health and improved wellbeing, ultimately resulting in emotional benefits for the whole family,' he said.</p>

<p>All products part of the new Spring collection are available online or at Biw W stores.</p>
